The paper deals with incremental learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. The paper proposes an algorithm to make rational inferences about the updated classifier with low computational complexity, which falls under the category of optimization and sensitivity analysis. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
